# VHS Tape: brain overview demo
# Quick overview of brain CLI capabilities

Output output/overview.webm

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20

Type "brain --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type ""
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "# Initialize a new project"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "brain init --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type ""
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "# Check project status"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "brain status --help"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Sleep 1s
